  <div class="field field-name-field-text-teaser field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>Do the exercises and learn the words for some accessories.</p></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p><a class="embed" href="http://gamedata.britishcouncil.org/d/ImageMatching_MTA5NTA=.xml">Exercise</a></p></div></div></div><div class="field-collection-container clearfix"><div class="field field-name-field-task field-type-field-collection field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"></div></div></div><div class=" group-tasks field-group-accordion field-group-accordion-wrapper effect-bounceslide"><h3 class="field-group-format-toggler accordion-item"><a href="#">Task 1</a></h3>
